when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16264,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-tool-routing.md\",\n          \"title\": \"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16263,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/finding-is-a-hypothesis.md\",\n          \"title\": \"A Finding Is a Hypothesis Until You Open the Cited Code\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never ground truth. | Prioritize when: only verdict discipline still holds: never soften an active blocker without new evidence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15815,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6626,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename\",\n          \"title\": \"Skill Rename [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"skill\",\n            \"workflows\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"007\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1498,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/024-sk-deep-research-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Specification: sk-deep-research Refinement [skilled-agent-orchestration/024-sk-deep-research-refinement/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1371,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/005-cli-codex-creation\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Specification: cli-gemini Model Consolidation + [03--commands-and-skills/005-cli-codex-creation/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"cli\",\n            \"model\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6625,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename\",\n          \"title\": \"Implementation [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename/plan]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"workflows\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"007\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 16994,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-spec-kit-internals/002-skill-advisor/002-skill-adv