{"type":"text","timestamp":1782897133466,"sessionID":"ses_0e30e0717ffe0AOyqAZM72PE2n","part":{"id":"prt_f1cf3218e001CRZT7dSUP6Wb7f","messageID":"msg_f1cf2f064001rOq2D69YIT41Z7","sessionID":"ses_0e30e0717ffe0AOyqAZM72PE2n","type":"text","text":"The deep-research contract requires command-owned state rather than an ad hoc loop, but the user’s boundary forbids writes outside the lineage directory. I’m checking the command/workflow files to identify the phase entrypoint that can honor the provided artifact override without running `resolveArtifactRoot`.","time":{"start":1782897123727,"end":1782897133465},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_04b6b978e94dc766016a44d9e39e5481958c165becafb49e0b","phase":"commentary"}}}}
