{"type":"text","timestamp":1782897265801,"sessionID":"ses_0e30e0717ffe0AOyqAZM72PE2n","part":{"id":"prt_f1cf547670015n50J1E4lQLnxl","messageID":"msg_f1cf525fe001Aj0hpNWyYcjgso","sessionID":"ses_0e30e0717ffe0AOyqAZM72PE2n","type":"text","text":"The live evidence supports several sharper corrections than the prior GPT lineage: Phase 0 is a real Mode-D firing point, ai-council route proof is a false-pass risk, and the plugin can mutate tool args but fail-closed semantics remain unproven. I’m going to create the lineage state, 10 iterations, registry/dashboard, and synthesis under `gpt-critical` only.","time":{"start":1782897264487,"end":1782897265798},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0314912b22540d7e016a44da706cd48191a5de6ab62df37a8b","phase":"commentary"}}}}
