erification-smoke/verification-smoke.md` -- Phase 005 failed/blocked smoke table.\n+- `005-gpt-verification-smoke/implementation-summary.md` -- verification summary and limitations.\n+- `006-host-hard-identity-fix5/decision-record.md` -- existing FIX-5 trigger.\n+- `001-deep-agent-router-and-orchestration/research/research.md` -- original root-cause and hard-identity ceiling.\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/007-gpt-behavioral-hardening-research/research/lineages/gpt-critical/deep-research-config.json","relativePath":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/007-gpt-behavioral-hardening-research/research/lineages/gpt-critical/deep-research-config.json","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/007-gpt-behavioral-hardening-research/research/lineages/gpt-critical/deep-research-config.json\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/007-gpt-behavioral-hardening-research/research/lineages/gpt-critical/deep-research-config.json\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/007-gpt-behavioral-hardening-research/research/lineages/gpt-critical/deep-research-config.json\n@@ -0,0 +1,25 @@\n+{\n+  \"schemaVersion\": \"deep-research-config/v1\",\n+  \"mode\": \"research\",\n+  \"sessionId\": \"fanout-gpt-critical-1782897047002-qhoaax\",\n+  \"lineageLabel\": \"gpt-critical\",\n+  \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n+  \"generation\": 1,\n+  \"specFolder\": \".opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/007-gpt-behavioral-hardening-research\",\n+  \"arti